The paper deals with image processing techniques for multimedia forensics, specifically in the area of printed document authentication. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also deals with classification algorithms, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with issues of security and fraud, which could fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
